<p
  style="
    font-family: 'Arial', 'Tahoma', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #e0e0f0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(128, 0, 128, 0.3);
  "
>
  Dear <%= name %>,
</p>
<p
  style="
    font-family: 'Arial', 'Tahoma', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #e0e0f0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(128, 0, 128, 0.3);
  "
>
  Thank you for joining Akkadli! We’re thrilled to have you on board as you take
  control of your business with our powerful management tools. With Akkadli, you
  can efficiently manage orders, products, and deliveries, and look forward to
  future automation features like automated order tracking and creation.
</p>
<p
  style="
    font-family: 'Arial', 'Tahoma', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #e0e0f0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(128, 0, 128, 0.3);
  "
>
  Here are your account details to get started:
</p>
<ul
  style="
    font-family: 'Arial', 'Tahoma', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #d3d3e8;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(128, 0, 128, 0.3);
    list-style-type: none;
    padding-left: 20px;
  "
>
  <li
    style="
      color: #d3a7f7;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 15px;
    "
  >
    <span style="color: #800080; font-weight: bold; position: absolute; left: 0"
      >•</span
    >
    Email: <%= email %>
  </li>
  <li
    style="
      color: #d3a7f7;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 15px;
    "
  >
    <span style="color: #800080; font-weight: bold; position: absolute; left: 0"
      >•</span
    >
    Login URL:
    <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" style="color: #d3a7f7; text-decoration: none"
      ><%= loginUrl %></a
    >
  </li>
</ul>
<p
  style="
    font-family: 'Arial', 'Tahoma', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #b3b3cc;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(128, 0, 128, 0.3);
    border-top: 1px solid #800080;
    text-align: center;
  "
>
  Thanks!<br />The Akkadli Team
</p>
